data.description: Charming ranch-style residence boasting three bedrooms and two bathrooms situated on a sizable lot. Features alley access at the rear, a spacious kitchen equipped with a gas stove, slate tile flooring, a pantry, and granite tile countertops, alongside all appliances. The master bedroom offers ample space, highlighted by a walk-in closet and a cozy sitting area. The roof was redone in 2022, and a partially finished basement with a pool table, included in the sale of the home.
